  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>We’re Hiring – Full-Time Customer Service & Heritage Representative📍 The Peranakan Club | Orchard Road The Peranakan Club is Singapore’s first integrated Peranakan living heritage destination — bringing together food, stories, culture, and community under one roof.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join The Peranakan Club as a Full-Time Customer Service & Heritage Representative to create meaningful guest experiences by delivering welcoming service, sharing cultural stories, and supporting daily operations in a vibrant heritage setting.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Greet guests warmly and deliver friendly, attentive customer service to enhance their experience</li><li>Assist guests with seating arrangements, taking orders, processing payments, and performing basic service tasks accurately</li><li>Share simple Peranakan heritage stories, food knowledge, and cultural insights to enrich guest understanding (training provided)</li><li>Support the smooth running of gallery tours, workshops, and special events as needed</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and create a calm, welcoming environment for guests and staff</li><li>Collaborate closely with kitchen and operations teams to ensure efficient daily service flow</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Comfortable communicating with guests in English; proficiency in Mandarin or Malay is a bonus</li><li>Interest in heritage, food, or community work</li><li>Willingness to work weekends and rotating shifts</li><li>Open to seniors, caregivers returning to work, career switchers, and first-time F&B workers</li><li>No prior experience required; training will be provided</li></ul><p>What We Offer</p><ul><li>Full-time stable employment</li><li>Supportive, care-first workplace culture</li><li>On-the-job training in service excellence and heritage storytelling</li><li>Career development opportunities</li><li>Meaningful work contributing to inclusive employment and cultural preservation</li></ul><p>📩 How to Apply</p><ul><li>WhatsApp your name, availability, and a short introduction to: 94761688 or email: khoo.christie@gmail.com</li></ul><p>Join us in keeping Peranakan heritage alive — one guest, one story, one shared meal at a time.</p>",
